{"tid":22611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友係我面前掉左份生日禮物","createTime":"2016-12-04T14:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T13:52:09.000Z","uid":7248,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aee5eaec5d7c719d3ed9bc61b875b226845a9df7","tid":22611,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日係我男朋友生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢平時好中意睇波 咁岩見到有本新書就即刻買左！<br />\n諗住佢一定好滿意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z14f0uZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz14f0uZ.jpg&h=0e665300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n送左比佢之後就叫佢拆黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知 佢一拆開 望一望我<br />\n男朋友: 你係咪特登架？<br />\n我:下？咩特登呀？你唔係中意喱隊球隊咩？<br />\n男:我中意嘅係曼聯<br />\n我:大家都係紅色姐 不用分得這樣細<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就掉左本書落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知我做錯左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96bdf0430bd9eb4832ec2ce8bdaa98c200af4c9","tid":22611,"uid":5306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"其實冇錯"},{"pid":"ffeade35d47c72e0040158d39f22666f5c68c258","tid":22611,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"中國隊都係紅包<br />\n下次買中國隊啦，平d<br />\n橫掂都係掉"},{"pid":"d72a95dd7a5e8ff93af85fc8d66ab9298a8c76d2","tid":22611,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:14:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國隊都係紅色<br />\n下次買中國隊啦，平d<br />\n橫掂都係掉</blockquote>"},{"pid":"139d0f9640672aa62d6fe6824ba6864e5faf84bf","tid":22611,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquot